      "description": "This driver-focused E46 M3 features the high-revving S54 inline-six, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized camshaft timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement to prevent floor pan fatigue and a recent rod bearing service. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, maintaining the sharp turn-in characteristic of the chassis. While it shows honest patina from road use, the mechanical synchronization and compression across all six cylinders remain within factory tolerances.",
